title.$t: EGE Red Carpet "Hard Man" by ASL Films

media$title.$t: EGE Red Carpet "Hard Man" by ASL Films

media$description.$t:
EG Entertainment (EGE) invites you to our 3rd annual Red Carpet event! 

This will be ASL Films' 7th full-length film release, and the Red Carpet event will bring the Deaf community together again for another glamorous Hollywood experience. ASL Films will premiere the film "Hard Man" directed by Mark Wood and acted by our well-known entertainer Andrew Vasnick, who also acted in "Gerald." The Red Carpet event will bring the Deaf community together again for another glamorous Hollywood experience. 

Buy Ticket via PayPal: http://www.evelinagaina.com. 
Production Company: http://www.aslfilms.com.
Collaboration: http://www.ideafnews.com & http://www.gladinc.org.

Please take a moment to visit our new Facebook Page and Click Like: http://www.facebook.com/EvelinaGainaEntertainment
